#- Who's the cutest kitty cat in kitty cat city?§0
§0I asked the king, the preacher and I even asked my mommy§0
§0They said they couldn't answer because kitty's pretty§0
§0But I told them that I'm pretty sure it's Reiko Mikami
#- This page is dedicated to the courage of the kitties§0
§0Who founded one night this town, kitty cat city§0
§0It was middle of summer, on a dark dog day§0
§0When they said, in this city may all pretty kitties stay!
